JReversi
-----------
A reversi (also known as Othello) game.

Written by Oli and RenÃ©.

Import into Eclipse IDE
-----------------------
Using Import Wizard: "File" -> "Import..." -> "Existings Projects into Workspace" then select root folder "JReversi"

Importent notes
---------------
You should run the applet by using the following VM-Arguments:

-Xmx512m -XX:+UseParallelGC

You can achieve this by adding them to your launch configuration in the "arguments" tab, Section "VM arguments".

Play the game
--------------
Start the StarterApplet.

Git-Hub link
------------
https://github.com/mtwords/JReversi
